casebody.data:
Friday, December 4, 1998

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

98-2298. Drake-Lassie v. State Farm Ins. Cos.

Franklin App. No. 98AP-40. This cause is pending before the court as a discretionary appeal. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application for dismissal be, and hereby is, granted.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
